RESULT: Power Supply Module to Load Module continuity tests both report an open circuit with unresolvable probe nodes. With the battery installed, the Load Input Cable (+) measures about 0.36 V relative to ground and the Load Input Cable (−) is near 0 V. Both the Main Load (lamp) and the Internal Indicator Lamp are not lit and show no observable internal faults.
