r unseated battery clip, a cracked solder joint, or a mis-terminated wire). Repairing or re-establishing this connection should restore a proper 12 V differential between PSU Output Cable (+) and PSU Output Cable (−), which in turn will allow the control and load modules to operate correctly.'
